OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FStaying warm
OL,6,Fand at times muggy, whilst also
OL,7,Fremaining rather cloudy and damp, with
OL,8,Fspells of rain and drizzle most
OL,9,Ffrequently affecting the west, but
OL,10,Fperhaps seen more widely towards dawn.
OL,11,FLight winds.
OL,12,
OL,13,CWednesday:FCloudy and damp during the
OL,14,Fmorning especially, but probably
OL,15,Ftending to become drier into the
OL,16,Fafternoon, with a greater chance of
OL,17,Fsome bright or sunny spells. Warm,
OL,18,Fwith light winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
