OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,6,FChangeable and often on the cloudy
OL,7,Fside through this period, with bands
OL,8,Fof rain making erratic progress
OL,9,Feastwards. Some warm sunny spells are
OL,10,Fstill expected, however, with
OL,11,Ftemperatures climbing.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
